  * **GitHub:** [Репозиторий PaddleDetection](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleDetection/)
  * **Документация:** [PP-YOLOE+ Documentation](https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleDetection/blob/release/2.8.1/configs/ppyoloe/README.md)



